    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそよろしくお願いします、山田さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you‚ Yamada-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでは、星見プロさんのグループと\n戦うことになりましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In I-UNITY‚ we battled against\nHoshimi Pro's group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "これからは、同じ事務所のメンバーとして\nよろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But from now on‚ we're members of the same agency.\nLet's work together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ⅢXは、ステージの完成度とビジュアルがウリの）\n（実力派アイドルグループだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（IIIX is known for their polished stage presence and visuals.）\n（They're a talented idol group.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（いろいろあったけど、今日からは同じ事務所の仲間だ）\n（俺もマネージャーとして、なんとか頑張らないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（There were some issues‚ but from today‚ we're fellow members of the same agency.）\n（As a manager‚ I have to do my best somehow…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
