      "text": "……ふん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmph.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "この際……と言うか、最初に言っておきますけど\n私達は便宜上、星見プロに籍を置いておくだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this case… or rather‚ I'll say it upfront.\nWe're simply putting ourselves under Hoshimi Pro for convenience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "一応あなたがマネージャーってことになってますけど\n全部、指示に従うつもりはありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're designated as the manager‚\nbut I won't be following your instructions entirely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "あと、それから\n私のこと山田って呼ぶの止めてくれません？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚\nCan you stop calling me Yamada?",
        "id": ""
      },
